<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[الانسلاع]</span>: انسلع: أي انشق، قال <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>من بارئ حِيْصَ ودامٍمُنْسَلِعْ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
